# Tokenomics of LLM Studio Token (LST) ðŸ’°

## Token Overview
LLM Studio Token (LST) is the native utility token that powers the platform ecosystem, incentivizes participation, and governs platform advancements.

## Token Distribution
- **Total Supply:** 1,000,000,000 LST
- **Team & Founders:** 20%
- **Community & Rewards:** 30%
- **Ecosystem Growth & Partnerships:** 25%
- **Staking & Governance:** 15%
- **Liquidity & Reserves:** 10%

## Use Cases
- **Transaction Fees:** Pay for AI-powered code generation and deployment services.
- **Staking Rewards:** Earn incentives by staking LST to secure the network.
- **Governance:** Vote on platform upgrades, feature prioritization, and ecosystem development.
- **Access:** Unlock premium features and priority support.

## Supply Details
- Deflationary mechanisms including quarterly token burns based on usage metrics.
- Inflation managed via staking rewards to encourage long-term participation.

## Burn Mechanisms
- Portion of transaction fees converted to LST will be burned periodically to reduce circulating supply.
- Additional burns linked to platform milestones and community events to promote token scarcity.

LLM Studio Token aligns incentives across users, developers, and stakeholders, fueling a sustainable and vibrant ecosystem.